- Tuesday: Tactical training + gym
- Wednesday: Game situations + conditioning
- Thursday: Position-specific work
- Friday: Pre-match tactical prep
- Saturday: Match
- Sunday: Off

Ages 17-25:
- Monday: Recovery session + video analysis
- Tuesday: Tactical training + strength
- Wednesday: High-intensity game prep + power
- Thursday: Tactical refinement + individual work
- Friday: Match preparation (light)
- Saturday/Sunday: Match
- Remaining day: Recovery/regeneration

